---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="I'm Bikash – I work in marketing and like building things on the internet. Originally from Koraput, Odisha."
>
  <section class="about-page section">
    <div class="container content-width">
      <header class="page-header">
        <p class="section-title">About</p>
        <h1>The story so far</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="lead">I'm Bikash – I work in marketing and like building things on the internet. I'm originally from Koraput, a small town in Odisha.</p>

        <h2>Background</h2>
        <p>I grew up watching and playing cricket – been following it since 2003. In 2015, I started a small business, and a year later I got my engineering certification.</p>
        <p>That same year I got into marketing and found it really interesting. I like how it mixes psychology with data – trying to understand why people buy things, how products get traction, and what makes some ideas spread while others don't.</p>

        <h2>What I do now</h2>
        <p>Since 2022, I've been at <a href="https://vempus.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vempus</a>, where I'm now building <a href="https://vemgram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vemgram</a> – a B2B platform connecting Indian manufacturers with retailers and buyers.</p>
        <p>I occasionally put things up on Product Hunt too – mostly small tools and experiments.</p>

        <h2>What I write about</h2>
        <p>Most of my writing is about marketing, consumer behavior, and business strategy. I try to break down things I've read or experienced into something useful.</p>
        <p>I'm a big believer in doing things consistently over a long period of time. Not very glamorous, but it tends to work.</p>

        <h2>Beyond work</h2>
        <p>When I'm not working, I'm usually watching cricket, reading about consumer psychology, or going down a rabbit hole about some random business model.</p>

        <h2>What I believe</h2>
        <div class="beliefs-grid">
          <div class="belief-card">
            <span class="belief-number">01</span>
            <p>The things you don't do tend to bother you more than the things you do.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="belief-card">
            <span class="belief-number">02</span>
            <p>Money is a tool – useful for what it unlocks, not as a scorecard.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="belief-card">
            <span class="belief-number">03</span>
            <p>Life is a lot like browser tabs – messy, overwhelming, but somehow it works.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="belief-card">
            <span class="belief-number">04</span>
            <p>Most problems I've worried about never actually happened.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="connect-cta">
          <p>Want to connect? Find me on <a href="https://twitter.com/bablukampo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/bikashkampo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href="/contact">get in touch</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.1875rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-content a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-accent) 40%, transparent);
    transition: text-decoration-color var(--transition);
  }

  .about-content a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .beliefs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .belief-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .belief-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .belief-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .beliefs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .connect-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .connect-cta p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
</style>
